snippet.title: In memory of TITAN Early Access Trailer (Master your enemy)
snippet.description:
All new Turn-Based/RTS Space Opera blend with procedural generated combat system and maps!
Master your enemies and become, the Commander.
 
Available Now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/787780/In_memory_of_TITAN/

Visit: https://valhallauniverse.com/titan for more information.
